data.description:
15  Sycamore Street, Greenfield 93927 - Sycamore 1833 - Plan A This popular, two-story home offers charming curb appeal and warmth. 
 The open living and dining space connects conveniently to a nice kitchen featuring a pantry and ample workspace. A mudroom with a half bath and a large closet to complete the downstairs space.  On the second floor, the owner's bedroom features a private bath with double vanity and a huge walk-in closet.  Three more bedrooms, a large laundry room with a folding counter, a hall full bath, and a walk-in linen closet round out this desirable plan. The home is amazing!  Close to the newer local parks, sports courts, schools & shopping centers with EZ access to the freeway & commutes to Salinas, Monterey, and beyond - The home is still under construction. It is to be completed End Of Sept. 2022
